screen_desc:
The screenshot shows an "Activity" page from a mobile application. The page is divided into two sections: "Upcoming" and "Past." 

- In the "Upcoming" section, there is an entry for "Rental Cars" scheduled for today, August 9, at 12:00 PM. An image of a car key with the Uber logo is displayed next to the entry.
- The "Past" section indicates that there is no recent activity with the message, "You don't have any recent activity."
- At the bottom of the screen, there is a navigation bar with icons for "Home," "Services," "Activity" (currently selected), and "Account."
